text: Yolanda Williams (born 15 July 1943) is a Cuban gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Cuba Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Havana Category:Pan American Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Cuba Category:Gymnasts at the 1963 Pan American Games Category:Gymnasts at the 1967 Pan American Games
